prompt:
You are a requirements rewriter.
Rewrite each requirement into clean natural language suitable for UML state diagram generation.

Return ONLY valid JSON with this schema:
{
  "rewritten_requirements": [
    {
      "source_requirement": "string",
      "rewritten_requirement": "The system shall ..."
    }
  ]
}

Rules:
1. Keep exactly the same number of requirements and same order.
2. Do not add new meaning.
3. Each rewritten requirement must start with "The system shall".
4. Keep them concise and implementation-neutral.

Input JSON:
{
  "functional_requirements": [
    {
      "requirement": "The security system can be configured by the homeowner during installation.",
      "evidence_quote": "The SafeHome security function enables the homeowner to configure the security system when it is installed..."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "The software monitors all sensors connected to the security system.",
      "evidence_quote": "monitors all sensors connected to the security system"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "The software interacts with the homeowner through the Internet, a PC, or a control panel.",
      "evidence_quote": "interacts with the homeowner through the Internet, a PC, or a control panel."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Each sensor is assigned a number and type during system configuration.",
      "evidence_quote": "Each sensor is assigned a number and type..."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "A master password can be programmed for arming and disarming the system.",
      "evidence_quote": "...a master password is programmed for arming and disarming the system"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Telephone numbers can be input for dialing when a sensor event occurs.",
      "evidence_quote": "...telephone number(s) are input for dialing when a sensor event occurs."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "The software invokes an audible alarm attached to the system when a sensor event is recognized.",
      "evidence_quote": "When a sensor event is recognized, the software invokes an audible alarm attached to the system"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "The software dials a telephone number of a monitoring service after a delay time specified by the homeowner.",
      "evidence_quote": "after a delay time that is specified by the homeowner during system configuration activities, the software dials a telephone number of a monitoring service..."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "The software redials a telephone number every 20 seconds until a connection is obtained.",
      "evidence_quote": "...The telephone number will be redialed every 20 seconds until telephone connection is obtained."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "The interface displays prompting messages and system status information on the control panel, PC, or browser window.",
      "evidence_quote": "The homeowner receives security information via a control panel, the PC, or a browser, collectively called an interface. The interface displays prompting messages and system status information..."
    }
  ]
}

